# Default path overrides (optional)

Copy values into your shell or `.env` for local development.

```bash
# Runtime storage root (default: ./storage)
# COH_STORAGE_ROOT=./storage

# Web UCS file store (default: $COH_STORAGE_ROOT/uploads)
# UCS_WEBAPP_UPLOADS=./storage/uploads

# SQLite database (default: $COH_STORAGE_ROOT/web/data/app.db)
# SQLITE_PATH=./storage/web/data/app.db

# Build output root (default: ./build)
# COH_BUILD_ROOT=./build
```

Production (Fly.io / Docker) typically sets `SQLITE_PATH=/data/app.db` and `UCS_WEBAPP_UPLOADS=/data/uploads` on a mounted volume — unchanged from prior deployments.
